=head1 NAME

OCMload - Collects Oracle Configuration Manager Reports

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This module retrieves the Oracle Configuration Manager reports.

=cut

debug ' Inside LOAD module, gathering Oracle Configuration Manager information'

call setAbbr('OCM')
if getSetting('NO_OCM')
 call purge('E','.',0)
else
{# Purge old reports
 call purge('E','.',1,600)

 # Insert OCM reports
 if getSetting('OCM_IN_USE')
  toc '%INCLUDE("',catFile('extern',concat(${CUR.PREFIX},'index.txt')),'")%'
}

